snippet: Tasia Foman scored 14 points, Kelsey Lang had a double-double and No. 16 Texas defeated Texas-San Antonio 76-43 on Saturday for its third straight victory....
lead_paragraph: Tasia Foman scored 14 points, Kelsey Lang had a double-double and No. 16 Texas defeated Texas-San Antonio 76-43 on Saturday for its third straight victory.
